OL,4,CGangs warning for pupils missing
OL,5,Cmajority of school
OL,6, There has been a big increase in
OL,7, children in England missing large
OL,8, amounts of school - on top of
OL,9, disruption from Covid, warns a report.
OL,11,FMore than 90,000 pupils missed over
OL,12,Fhalf their lessons in the autumn term,
OL,13,Fsaid the Centre for Social Justice.
OL,15,FThey could be "extremely vulnerable to
OL,16,Fbeing picked up by gangs", said think
OL,17,Ftank founder Sir Iain Duncan Smith.
OL,19,FThe report warned these children would
OL,20,Fstruggle to ever catch up when they
OL,21,Fwere so "severely absent".
